{"tid":440668,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「國民待遇」嚇怕台人","createTime":"2017-10-19T03:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T03:46:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d9dcc45a34ae9b8a15335b302e4d8c8a3fd6c04b","tid":440668,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T03:45:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20187420&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20187420%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171019&d=fzrADbtbblIeUtXf8kvpxFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=42d1cb67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20187420%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171019&h=31e7e260\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20187420&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171019</a><br />\n<br />\n「國民待遇」嚇怕台人<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171019/large/a0405a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171019%2Flarge%2Fa0405a.gif&h=40837b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李明哲（左二）身陷內地刑網，中共的手段令台灣人恐懼。　資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】兩岸關係因九二共識爭議陷入低潮，北京今年初微調對台政策，強化軟功加大利誘，研究賦予台人「國民待遇」，有評論形容，大陸給予台人「國民待遇」，令人毛骨悚然，民進黨前黨工、NGO工作者李明哲身陷內地刑網，就是中國「（類）國民待遇」的活生生鐵證。<br />\n<br />\n賦予台灣人國民待遇政策，始於今年1月中共對台工作會議。政協主席俞正聲要求內地各部門做好對台工作，研究推出便利台灣民眾在大陸求學、就業、創業、生活等政策。大陸海協會長陳德銘5月透露風聲，給予台人特別是年輕一代前往大陸求學、就業、創業等「接近大陸人民的各種待遇」。<br />\n<br />\n習昨宣讀十九大報告，不僅對政策來個一錘定音，還「賣大包」，由陳德銘所說的類國民待遇，逐步加碼至和大陸國民待遇等齊，「為台灣同胞在大陸學習、創業、就業、生活提供與大陸同胞同等的待遇」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者盧燕儀"},{"pid":"c716df5ab0a01c4970d935c8651fb57ee1f1a4f7","tid":440668,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T03:46:57.000Z","msg":"買菜刀實名登記<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}